dct_description_sm:
This feature class contains land parcel boundaries delineated for property tax
        assessment purposes. Parcels are modeled as planimetric polygons in a seamless fabric
        comprising the spatial extent of the County of Kern, in the State of California, as of
        2009.
dct_creator_sm:
Kern County Assessor's Office, Assessment Standards Division, Mapping
          Section.
